      "text_block": {
        "title": "孙坚",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f2_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "正东方向来了一彪人马。打头的是孙坚，宽额阔面，虎背熊腰。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f2_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "十七岁那年他在钱塘一个人吓跑了十几个海贼，还追上去砍翻了一个。从此郡县知名。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0016,
        "y": 0.3306,
        "w": 0.5016,
        "h": 0.3369
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f3",
      "scene_id": "cp002_p02_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp002-p02-page-01-f3",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "夺槊",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f3_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "孙坚第一个登上城头，连斩黄巾军二十余人。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f3_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "敌将挺槊冲来。孙坚侧身攥杆，拽人下马，调头反刺，一气呵成。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.5032,
        "y": 0.3306,
        "w": 0.4952,
